title: Number of divorces in Sweden 2008 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of divorces. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
Overall Number of divorces has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012 and 2013.
Maximum Number of divorces, about 26933.0 was reported at Year 2013
The lowest Number of divorces, of value 22580.0 was reported at Year 2008
min_summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of divorces. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
Overall Number of divorces has increased over the Year.

Number of divorces is gradually increasing from 2008 to 2010, roughly constant from 2010 to 2012, slightly increasing from 2012 to 2013, slightly decreasing from 2013 to 2015, roughly constant from 2015 to 2017, and lastly roughly increasing from 2017 to 2018.
